---
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="bg-surface py-[120px]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6">

    <div class="mb-16 flex flex-col gap-4">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-orange">How It Works</p>
      <h2 class="max-w-xl text-[42px] font-semibold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-navy">
        From CV upload to learning roadmap in minutes.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 border border-[#e8eaed]">
        <span class="text-[56px] font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight text-[#e8eaed]">01</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy">Upload your CV</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
            We extract your work history, education, and every skill you've
            built across your career automatically.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 border border-[#e8eaed]">
        <span class="text-[56px] font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight text-[#e8eaed]">02</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy">Add a target role</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
            Paste a job description or drop in a job posting URL. We parse the
            full requirement set so nothing gets missed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl bg-navy p-8">
        <span class="text-[56px] font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight text-white">03</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Get your roadmap</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-white/60">
            We generate a step-by-step learning path tailored to your specific
            skill gaps — not generic advice.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
